33f307efebd680cd286ef42cdf753","tid":803012,"uid":168156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"6隻黃個月餅咪好撚大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78eb3a000580aff590ca62c3d665ffcc3883de29","tid":803012,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aff13da7d5518e61ae5d29484790af41adafa1a1","tid":803012,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"一個月餅切十二件咪有十二黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚抵即刻買返盒"},{"pid":"a2c75245258ddfc0c223182945ce074548ca44c6","tid":803012,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"P圖條友唔小心姐"},{"pid":"359bdf06f5cfcb5bed2501ff265127e5b101608b","tid":803012,"uid":132461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"律師梁永鏗表示，餐牌圖片與實物不符，有機會牴觸商品說明條例，屬誤導性遺漏的不良營商手法，他解釋說：「市民睇到個廣告或餐牌先去買，點知買咗唔係嗰樣嘢！」。即使商戶餐牌寫有「相片只供參考」字句，也不能用作「擋箭牌」，「如果相片係有五粒魚蛋，但實物得三粒，都有可能違例。」<br />\n<br />\n創意宣傳湧現<br />\n另外，海關關長張雲正昨在電台節目上指，店舖展出貨品圖片曾經過處理，是否違例的決定因素之一，是店方有否告知消費者實物「未必係一樣」，若圖片與實物有極端差別海關亦會跟進，但會個別考慮檢控。"},{"pid":"9f5a00d0bfceea0ef94aac1fb5e5ef3ac778018e","tid":803012,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aff13da7d5518e61ae5d29484790af41adafa1a1","tid":803012,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"一個月餅切十二件咪有十二黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚抵即刻買返盒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"3隻黃切6刀=6黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}